{"talk":{"id":53583,"name":"Anna Piperal: What a digital government looks like","description":"What if you never had to fill out paperwork again? In Estonia, this is a reality: citizens conduct nearly all public services online, from starting a business to voting from their laptops, thanks to the nation's ambitious post-Soviet digital transformation known as \"e-Estonia.\" One of the program's experts, Anna Piperal, explains the key design principles that power the country's \"e-government\" -- and shows why the rest of the world should follow suit to eradicate outdated bureaucracy and regain citizens' trust.","slug":"anna_piperal_what_a_digital_government_looks_like","recorded_at":"2019-07-20 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-01-09 15:50:40","updated_at":"2021-10-22 23:16:00","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":603,"name":"TEDSummit 2019"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/960f27c683c19e075074ddfc2441b83a04cf595e_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/960f27c683c19e075074ddfc2441b83a04cf595e_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/960f27c683c19e075074ddfc2441b83a04cf595e_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/960f27c683c19e075074ddfc2441b83a04cf595e_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/36a66e4bbd76b0cdf086dca351cf40b525e6f9ed_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnnaPiperal_2019T-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6863628,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnnaPiperal_2019T-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":19011056,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnnaPiperal_2019T-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","fil